    "Therefore, accurately predicting the spread pattern of the coronavirus is crucial for global pandemic preparation and management.",
    "In addition to traditional methods, deep learning techniques have been employed to successfully forecast trends in COVID-19 infections.",
    "In this study, several deep learning models, including CNN, CNN-LSTM, and LSTM, were used to predict the count of coronavirus patients.",
    "The functionality of these models was compared with previously developed deep learning frameworks, and substantial improvements in the forecasting performance were observed.",
    "These models can be easily implemented to predict the data for all countries worldwide."
